==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hicksite
<hw>Hicks"ite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A member or follower
of the ⟦ldquo⟧liberal⟦rdquo⟧ party, headed by Elias <xex>Hicks</xex>,
which, because of a change of views respecting the divinity of Christ
and the Atonement, seceded from the conservative portion of the Society
of Friends in the United States, in 1827.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hickup</ent>⟦br⟧
